com.fasterxml.transistore.basic

Class BasicTSKeyConverter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.fasterxml.clustermate.api.EntryKeyConverter<BasicTSKey>
      • com.fasterxml.transistore.basic.BasicTSKeyConverter

  • public class BasicTSKeyConverter
extends com.fasterxml.clustermate.api.EntryKeyConverter<BasicTSKey>
    Default EntryKeyConverter used with Basic TransiStore types.

    In addition class implements encoding and decoding of the entry keys (of type BasicTSKey): uses BasicTSConstants.TS_QUERY_PARAM_PARTITION_ID in addition to path (which is regular filename).
